<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>Fluxbox</application></title>

<para>Install <application>Fluxbox</application> by running the following 
commands:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>patch -Np1 -i ../fluxbox-0.1.14-gcc33.patch &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-kde --enable-gnome &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

